<p>I was invited to give a talk at the <a href="https://www.aps.org/units/damop/meetings/meeting.cfm?name=DAMOP16">2016 Division of Atomic, Molecular, and Optical Physics meeting</a> on integrating computation across the curriculum. In that talk, I mentioned a number of papers and resources. Below are all the papers and resources:</p>

